-- Sanofi Planning Further Acquisitions, Board Member Tells Boersen
-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 2012-05-31T17:43:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-31/sanofi-planning-further-acquisitions-board-member-tells-boersen.html
Hanspeter Spek, President of Global
Operations at  Sanofi (SAN)  said the company is considering additional
acquisitions,  Boersen Zeitung  reported citing an interview.  Spek said the company had a very strong free and operating
cash flow and is ready for “external growth,” the newspaper
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
